title: Ungodly Que times in Normal - Draft
body:
So while riot's region transfers are down I made a new account since I moved from NA to Australia. I've noticed that the que times are just atrocious over here. Usually a game takes 3-4 minutes to find in NA while over here in OCE I've found myself waiting for forty minutes before I started a new que, now I've waited eleven minutes in this new que. Is it the fact that I'm level thirteen right now, or is there something else that's wrong here. I understand that it's currently 11:24pm where I'm at right now in Western Australia but fifty plus minutes is rediculous.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
